67
00:05:41,300 --> 00:05:47,880
Him? Yeah. The guy in this picture was definitely in here that night.

68
00:05:48,380 --> 00:05:51,940
Was he alone? I'm not sure. I really don't remember.

69
00:05:52,520 --> 00:05:56,920
So you remember that he was here, but you don't recall if he was here with someone or

70
00:05:56,920 --> 00:06:00,020
