121
00:09:32,800 --> 00:09:38,580
You need to shut up. At your age, old man, you should be at home playing with your grandkids.

122
00:09:41,340 --> 00:09:43,940
Hey! I still want an answer!

123
00:09:45,800 --> 00:09:46,280
(grunting)

124
00:09:51,300 --> 00:09:51,940
- Hold it!

125
00:09:54,960 --> 00:09:57,960
You know, I trained as a border patrol officer.

126
00:09:58,180 --> 00:09:58,860
- It really hurts.

127
00:09:59,200 --> 00:10:01,280
- Speak up, why'd you try to push me earlier?

128
00:10:01,720 --> 00:10:03,160
- I, I don't know.

129
00:10:03,580 --> 00:10:05,940
- Don't you dare try to pull one over on me.

130
00:10:07,800 --> 00:10:09,120
- Somebody asked me to do it.

131
00:10:09,240 --> 00:10:09,980
- Who was it?

132
00:10:10,140 --> 00:10:11,280
- It was some big guy.

133
00:10:12,520 --> 00:10:14,140
What do you mean, a big guy?

134
00:10:14,560 --> 00:10:16,580
A guy I met in the subway paid me

135
00:10:16,580 --> 00:10:18,740
to push you off the platform and onto the tracks.

136
00:10:19,160 --> 00:10:20,600
