Oh!

146
00:11:10,860 --> 00:11:15,440
I brought you scotch, single malt, the really good stuff you liked.

147
00:11:16,160 --> 00:11:17,740
You deserve it, my friend.

148
00:11:25,080 --> 00:11:25,960
It's okay.

149
00:11:27,160 --> 00:11:28,760
You can have a drink now.

150
00:11:35,480 --> 00:11:37,160
You can count on me, Richard.

151
00:11:37,660 --> 00:11:39,100
As God is my witness,

152
00:11:39,600 --> 00:11:41,740
I'll identify the guy who did this.

153
00:11:42,340 --> 00:11:43,300
I swear it.

154
00:11:44,960 --> 00:11:47,620
I'll uncover Johan's true identity.

155
00:12:01,900 --> 00:12:05,920
So listen to this, Doctor. I finally told my husband what I think.

156
00:12:06,180 --> 00:12:10,040
I said that his cheating on me is a disease that's festering inside him.

157
00:12:10,140 --> 00:12:13,280
Then I told that ape that he's the one who should be sitting here and counting.

158
00:12:13,300 --> 00:12:14,280
It's like, not me.

159
00:12:16,820 --> 00:12:19,000
Doctor, did you hear what I said?

160
00:12:19,480 --> 00:12:19,720
- Hmm?

161
00:12:20,220 --> 00:12:21,640
Why, yes, I did.

162
00:12:22,100 --> 00:12:22,680
Go ahead.

163
00:12:23,180 --> 00:12:24,180
- Well, then tell me.

164
00:12:24,300 --> 00:12:26,080
If my husband keeps this up,

165
00:12:26,180 --> 00:12:28,680
I feel like my depression's only going to get worse,

166
00:12:28,680 --> 00:12:29,240
isn't it?

167
00:12:29,660 --> 00:12:30,300
- Well, no.

168
00:12:30,820 --> 00:12:33,480
I don't believe you're really clinically depressed at all.

169
00:12:34,000 --> 00:12:34,480
- Huh?

170
00:12:34,980 --> 00:12:37,480
- Honestly, I'm more concerned about your husband's actions

171
00:12:37,480 --> 00:12:39,000
than I am with your mental state.

172
00:12:39,160 --> 00:12:41,940
We must find out why he's giving you the silent treatment.

173
00:12:43,300 --> 00:12:45,520
The Big Lug doesn't know which end is up.

174
00:12:45,840 --> 00:12:47,660
Please, Doctor, I beg of you.

175
00:12:47,960 --> 00:12:49,860
Please make some time to see my husband.

176
00:12:50,140 --> 00:12:51,040
Of course I will.

177
00:12:51,320 --> 00:12:53,200
I have a slot open the day after tomorrow

178
00:12:53,200 --> 00:12:54,760
at five o'clock in the afternoon.

179
00:12:55,000 --> 00:12:55,340
All right?

180
00:12:55,940 --> 00:12:57,800
Thank you. I'll tell him tonight.

181
00:13:00,520 --> 00:13:02,220
Make sure you give that cheating jerk

182
00:13:02,220 --> 00:13:03,460
a good talking to, Doctor.

183
00:13:03,720 --> 00:13:05,420
Don't hold back. You got that?

184
00:13:19,920 --> 00:13:23,080
Doctor, that was the last of your appointments for today.

185
00:13:23,380 --> 00:13:26,380
Good. Thank you very much, Merith. See you tomorrow, then.

186
00:13:26,800 --> 00:13:28,200
All right, then. Good night.

187
00:13:28,560 --> 00:13:29,980
