193
00:13:48,120 --> 00:13:49,400
(phone ringing)

194
00:13:53,080 --> 00:13:54,740
- Hello, Dr. Gillen?

195
00:13:55,640 --> 00:13:57,100
It's Dr. Reichwein.

196
00:13:58,460 --> 00:13:59,940
I saw today's paper.

197
00:14:01,440 --> 00:14:03,680
Why yes, I saw your newspaper ad in there.

198
00:14:04,720 --> 00:14:08,020
Let's talk about our memories of cheating, Rudy.

199
00:14:08,920 --> 00:14:11,800
So you really think if Dr. Tenma sees this message

200
