244
00:16:30,240 --> 00:16:31,460
He was a large one.

245
00:16:31,620 --> 00:16:33,020
So he was a big man.

246
00:16:33,500 --> 00:16:36,720
Oh yeah, and I heard he was pretty big downstairs, too.

247
00:16:40,260 --> 00:16:41,820
Doctor, excuse me.

248
00:16:43,300 --> 00:16:45,860
if it would be all right for me to leave early today?

249
00:16:46,120 --> 00:16:47,240
- Yes, I remember that.

250
00:16:47,480 --> 00:16:49,100
You said you needed to leave at five.

251
00:16:49,480 --> 00:16:50,300
That'll be fine.

252
00:16:50,500 --> 00:16:52,080
The only appointment I have left today

253
00:16:52,080 --> 00:16:53,320
is Mrs. Hess's husband.

254
00:16:53,880 --> 00:16:55,540
Are you going on a date, Merith?

255
