00:22:08,480 --> 00:22:09,820
[PANTING]

330
00:22:10,160 --> 00:22:10,900
Wait.

331
00:22:11,480 --> 00:22:13,720
Why aren't you--

332
00:22:14,400 --> 00:22:15,900
Get out of here now!

333
00:22:16,680 --> 00:22:18,380
Dr. Tenma.

